    # voice audio.kano_vs9_line21
    # k "After a nostalgic day like this, I can’t think of a better way to end things! That thunderstorm was a blessing!"
    voice audio.kano_vs9_line21
    k "度过这样怀旧的一天后，我想不出更好的收尾方式了！那场雷雨真是天赐良机！"
# game/script_neutral.rpy:2087
